steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jit008" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jit008" display
When I add new column with Name "jitcol008" Type "datetime" for Table name "jit008"
When I open popup to see column infos Name "jitcol008" of table with Name "jit008"
Then I should see checkbox popup Name "Required,Unique" is unchecked
When I update popup with textarea Name "Comment" to value "Column testing"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Required"
When I check checkbox popup Name "Unique"
